flowRoot.flowPara: The July AWPUG Meetup will be held at the Texas Tribune., as always. Remember to always bring your towel, and DON'T PANIC.
We're hiring Python devs at uStudio! Proficiency in Python would be nice.
We need books. Books are great for giveaways, except for CouchDB books because no one has any taste.
I'm looking to start a Node.js and MongoDB project, and hopefully we'll be able to write a new messaging protocol.
We are needing more Armstrong volunteers. Join us if you want to work on next-gen Django for news!
